<refentry xml:id="reflectionclass.getdoccomment" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>ReflectionClass::getDocComment</refname>
  <refpurpose>获取文档注释</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>

 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
  <methodsynopsis role="ReflectionClass">
   <modifier>public</modifier> <type class="union"><type>string</type><type>false</type></type><methodname>ReflectionClass::getDocComment</methodname>
   <void/>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <para>
   从类中获取文档注释。文档注释以 <literal>/**</literal> 开头，后跟空格。
   如果类定义上方有多个文档注释，则采用最接近该类的注释。
  </para>

 </refsect1>

 <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  &no.function.parameters;
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <para>
   如果存在则返回文档注释，否则返回 &false;。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1 role="examples">
  &reftitle.examples;
  <para>
   <example>
    <title><methodname>ReflectionClass::getDocComment</methodname> 例子</title>
    <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
/**
 * A test class
 *
 * @param  foo bar
 * @return baz
 */
class TestClass { }

$rc = new ReflectionClass('TestClass');
var_dump($rc->getDocComment());
?>
]]>
    </programlisting>
    &example.outputs;
    <screen>
<![CDATA[
string(61) "/** 
 * A test class
 *
 * @param  foo bar
 * @return baz
 */"
]]>
    </screen>
   </example>
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1 role="seealso">
  &reftitle.seealso;
  <para>
   <simplelist>
    <member><methodname>ReflectionClass::getName</methodname></member>
   </simplelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>

</refentry>
